They absolutely do not know what happened.
Honorable senators, the words "continuity" and "dedication" are fashionable in our speeches.
In the next two weeks, let us begin to think about how we will deal with the situation of independent senators.
If we do not, I will create my own committee of parliamentarians who are interested in international affairs.
